(13, 'Royal Canin Kitten 400gm Cat Food', 6, 0, 0, NULL, NULL, 'no', NULL, 0, 0, 0, 0, '0', 'IT020658', 'Pcs', 'single', NULL, '1740220353.jpg', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '<p data-start=\"860\" data-end=\"1481\">Royal Canin Kitten 400g Cat Food is specifically designed to meet the nutritional needs of kittens from 4 to 12 months of age. During this critical growth phase, kittens require a diet that supports their developing immune system, promotes healthy digestion, and provides the energy needed for playful activities. This premium dry food formula includes highly digestible proteins, an optimal blend of vitamins and minerals, and antioxidants like vitamins C and E to bolster natural defenses. The kibble\'s size and texture are tailored for a kitten\'s small mouth, making it easy to chew and enjoy.</p>\r\n<p data-start=\"1483\" data-end=\"1496\"><strong data-start=\"1483\" data-end=\"1496\">Features:</strong></p>\r\n<ul data-start=\"1498\" data-end=\"2183\">\r\n<li data-start=\"1498\" data-end=\"1650\"><strong data-start=\"1500\" data-end=\"1526\">Immune System Support:</strong> Enriched with a patented complex of antioxidants, including vitamins C and E, to strengthen your kitten\'s natural defenses.</li>\r\n<li data-start=\"1651\" data-end=\"1799\"><strong data-start=\"1653\" data-end=\"1674\">Digestive Health:</strong> Contains highly digestible proteins and prebiotics to support a balanced intestinal flora and promote optimal stool quality.</li>\r\n<li data-start=\"1800\" data-end=\"1946\"><strong data-start=\"1802\" data-end=\"1821\">Healthy Growth:</strong> Provides an adapted level of protein, vitamins, and minerals to meet the energy needs of kittens during their growth period.</li>\r\n<li data-start=\"1947\" data-end=\"2073\"><strong data-start=\"1949\" data-end=\"1967\">Dental Health:</strong> The unique kibble design helps reduce dental plaque and tartar formation, supporting overall oral health.</li>\r\n<li data-start=\"2074\