(14, 'Kitchen Flavor Grain Free Cat Food With Real Meat Cubes Food 1.5kg', 7, 0, 0, NULL, NULL, 'no', NULL, 0, 0, 0, 0, '0', 'TU12AB', 'Pcs', 'variation', NULL, '1742642021.webp', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '[\"4\"]', NULL, '[]', NULL, '<p data-start=\"931\" data-end=\"1542\">The Grain Free with Real Meat Cubes 1.5kg Adult Cat Food is meticulously crafted to cater to the nutritional needs of adult cats. Free from grains, this formula is ideal for felines with sensitivities, ensuring easy digestion and reduced risk of allergies. The inclusion of real meat cubes offers a high-quality protein source, essential for muscle development and overall health. Natural ingredients promote a lustrous coat and healthy skin, while the exclusion of pork aligns with specific dietary preferences. This complete and balanced diet ensures your cat thrives with every meal.</p>\r\n<p data-start=\"1544\" data-end=\"1557\"><strong data-start=\"1544\" data-end=\"1557\">Features:</strong></p>\r\n<ul data-start=\"1559\" data-end=\"2018\">\r\n<li data-start=\"1559\" data-end=\"1655\"><strong data-start=\"1561\" data-end=\"1584\">Grain-Free Formula:</strong> Perfect for cats with grain sensitivities, promoting better digestion.</li>\r\n<li data-start=\"1656\" data-end=\"1753\"><strong data-start=\"1658\" data-end=\"1683\">High-Quality Protein:</strong> Real meat cubes provide essential amino acids for muscle maintenance.</li>\r\n<li data-start=\"1754\" data-end=\"1848\"><strong data-start=\"1756\" data-end=\"1780\">Natural Ingredients:</strong> Supports skin health and a shiny coat without artificial additives.</li>\r\n<li data-start=\"1849\" data-end=\"1921\"><strong data-start=\"1851\" data-end=\"1863\">No Pork:</strong> Adheres to specific dietary requirements and preferences.</li>\r\n<li data-start=\"1922\" data-end=\"2018\"><strong data-start=\"1924\" data-end=\"1960\">Complete and Balanced Nutrition:</strong> Meets all dietary needs of adult cats for optimal health.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p>