(74, 'Virbac Epiotic Salicylic Acid Ear Cleanser (100 ml)', NULL, 0, 0, NULL, NULL, 'no', NULL, 0, 0, 0, 0, '0', 'IT020650', 'Pcs', 'single', NULL, '17401447311457845464.jpeg', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '<p data-start=\"514\" data-end=\"971\">Virbac Epiotic is a patented ear cleanser formulated with salicylic acid to help maintain ear hygiene in both dogs and cats. Its gentle, non-irritating solution effectively removes debris, wax, and excess moisture, helping to prevent or manage otitis externa. Epiotic&rsquo;s patented anti-odor technology neutralizes unpleasant smells, while its mild pH and soothing properties make it suitable for routine use, even on sensitive ears.</p>\r\n<p data-start=\"973\" data-end=\"1003\"><strong data-start=\"973\" data-end=\"1001\">Key Benefits &amp; Features:</strong></p>\r\n<ol data-start=\"1004\" data-end=\"1589\">\r\n<li data-start=\"1004\" data-end=\"1136\"><strong data-start=\"1007\" data-end=\"1034\">Salicylic Acid Formula:</strong>\r\n<ul data-start=\"1040\" data-end=\"1136\">\r\n<li data-start=\"1040\" data-end=\"1136\">Aids in dissolving ear wax and debris, reducing the risk of bacterial and fungal infections.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</li>\r\n<li data-start=\"1137\" data-end=\"1232\"><strong data-start=\"1140\" data-end=\"1174\">Patented Anti-Odor Technology:</strong>\r\n<ul data-start=\"1180\" data-end=\"1232\">\r\n<li data-start=\"1180\" data-end=\"1232\">Neutralizes ear odor, promoting a fresher smell.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</li>\r\n<li data-start=\"1233\" data-end=\"1335\"><strong data-start=\"1236\" data-end=\"1264\">Gentle &amp; Non-Irritating:</strong>\r\n<ul data-start=\"1270\" data-end=\"1335\">\r\n<li data-start=\"1270\" data-end=\"1335\">Ideal for routine cleaning, even in pets with sensitive ears.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</li>\r\n<li data-start=\"1336\" data-end=\"1480\"><strong data-start=\"1339\" data-end=\"1376\">Pre-Treatment for Otitis Externa:</strong>\r\n<ul data-start=\"1382\" data-end=\"1480\">\r\n<li data-start=\"1382\" data-end=\"1480\">Helps prepare the ear canal for additional treatments if needed, as advised by a veterinarian.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</li>\r\n<li data-start=\"1481\" data-end=\"1589\"><strong data-start=\"1484\" data-end=\"1505\">Easy Application:</strong>\r\n<ul data-start=\"1511\" data-end=\"1589\">\r\n<li data-start=\"1511\" data-end=\"1589\">Comes in a convenient 100 ml bottle with a nozzle for controlled dispensing.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</li>\r\n</ol>\r\n<hr data-start=\"1591\" data-end=\"1594\" />\r\n<h2 data-start=\"1596\" data-end=\"1617\">Usage Instructions</h2>\r\n<ol data-start=\"1619\" data-end=\"2153\">\r\n<li data-start=\"1619\" data-end=\"1682\"><strong data-start=\"1622\" data-end=\"1637\">Shake Well:</strong>\r\n<ul data-start=\"1643\" data-end=\"1682\">\r\n<li data-start=\"1643\" data-end=\"1682\">Gently shake the bottle before use.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</li>\r\n<li data-start=\"1683\" data-end=\"1778\"><strong data-start=\"1686\" data-end=\"1696\">Apply:</strong>\r\n<ul data-start=\"1702\" data-end=\"1778\">\r\n<li data-start=\"1702\" data-end=\"1778\">Tilt your pet&rsquo;s head slightly and apply the solution into the ear canal.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</li>\r\n<li data-start=\"1779\" data-end=\"1877\"><strong data-start=\"1782\" data-end=\"1794\">Massage:</strong>\r\n<ul data-start=\"1800\" data-end=\"1877\">\r\n<li data-start=\"1800\" data-end=\"1877\">Gently massage the base of the ear for about 30 seconds to loosen debris.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</li>\r\n<li data-start=\"1878\" data-end=\"2019\"><strong data-start=\"1881\" data-end=\"1902\">Wipe Away Excess:</strong>\r\n<ul data-start=\"1908\" data-end=\"2019\">\r\n<li data-start=\"1908\" data-end=\"2019\">Allow your pet to shake its head, then wipe away any residual liquid with a clean cotton pad or soft cloth.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</li>\r\n</ol>\r\n<table class=\"table table-bordered \" style=\"border-collapse: collapse; display: none; width: 100%;\">\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td style=\"width: 50%;\">Title 1</td>\r\n<td style=\"width: 50%;\">&nbsp;</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td style=\"width: 50%;\">Title 2</td>\r\n<td style=\"width: 50%;\">&nbsp;</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td style=\"width: 50%;\">Title 3</td>\r\n<td style=\"width: 50%;\">&nbsp;</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>', '<p data-start=\"514\" data-end=\"971\">Virbac Epiotic is a patented ear cleanser formulated with salicylic acid to help maintain ear hygiene in both dogs and cats. Its gentle, non-irritating solution effectively removes debris, wax, and excess moisture, helping to prevent or manage otitis externa. Epiotic&rsquo;s patented anti-odor technology neutralizes unpleasant smells, while its mild pH and soothing properties make it suitable for routine use, even on sensitive ears.</p>\r\n<p data-start=\"973\" data-end=\"1003\"><strong data-start=\"973\" data-end=\"1001\">Key Benefits &amp; Features:</strong></p>\r\n<ol data-start=\"1004\" data-end=\"1589\">\r\n<li data-start=\"1004\" data-end=\"1136\"><strong data-start=\"1007\" data-end=\"1034\">Salicylic Acid Formula:</strong>\r\n<ul data-start=\"1040\" data-end=\"1136\">\r\n<li data-start=\"1040\" data-end=\"1136\">Aids in dissolving ear wax and debris, reducing the risk of bacterial and fungal infections.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</li>\r\n<li data-start=\"1137\" data-end=\"1232\"><strong data-start=\"1140\" data-end=\"1174\">Patented Anti-Odor Technology:</strong>\r\n<ul data-start=\"1180\" data-end=\"1232\">\r\n<li data-start=\"1180\" data-end=\"1232\">Neutralizes ear odor, promoting a fresher smell.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</li>\r\n<li data-start=\"1233\" data-end=\"1335\"><strong data-start=\"1236\" data-end=\"1264\">Gentle &amp; Non-Irritating:</strong>\r\n<ul data-start=\"1270\" data-end=\"1335\">\r\n<li data-start=\"1270\" data-end=\"1335\">Ideal for routine cleaning, even in pets with sensitive ears.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</li>\r\n<li data-start=\"1336\" data-end=\"1480\"><strong data-start=\"1339\" data-end=\"1376\">Pre-Treatment for Otitis Ex