(122, 'Transparent Pet Carrier Bag with Breathable Design and Shoulder Strap', NULL, 0, 0, NULL, NULL, 'flat', 200, 0, 0, 1, 0, '0', 'IT020619', 'Pcs', 'single', NULL, '17403911911361976365.jpeg', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '<p>Keep your furry friend comfortable and secure with this Transparent Pet Carrier Bag. The clear front panel offers excellent visibility, while multiple ventilation holes ensure ample airflow. Equipped with a sturdy handle and an adjustable shoulder strap, it&rsquo;s perfect for daily commutes or vet visits. Crafted from durable materials, this carrier combines style and function, making travel easier for both you and your pet.<br /><br /></p>\r\n<table class=\"table table-bordered \" style=\"border-collapse: collapse; display: none; width: 100%;\">\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td style=\"width: 50%;\">Title 1</td>\r\n<td style=\"width: 50%;\">&nbsp;</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td style=\"width: 50%;\">Title 2</td>\r\n<td style=\"width: 50%;\">&nbsp;</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td style=\"width: 50%;\">Title 3</td>\r\n<td style=\"width: 50%;\">&nbsp;</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>', '<p>Make every trip a breeze with our Transparent Pet Carrier Bag, designed to provide both comfort and convenience. The semi-hard, clear front panel lets you and your pet see each other, helping reduce anxiety during travel. With strategically placed ventilation holes and mesh side openings, your cat or small dog enjoys plenty of fresh air. The ergonomic handle and adjustable shoulder strap allow for easy carrying, whether you&rsquo;re heading to the vet, running errands, or embarking on a road trip.<br /><br />Constructed with durable materials, this carrier stands up to daily wear and tear. A secure zipper closure ensures your pet stays safely inside, while the lightweight design minimizes strain on your shoulders. Plus, the removable, easy-to-clean interior pad adds a layer of comfort for your pet and simplifies cleaning. Stylish and func