(125, 'Topicure Natural Spray (75 ml)  Comprehensive Topical Cure for Livestock', NULL, 0, 0, NULL, NULL, 'no', NULL, 0, 0, 0, 0, '0', 'IT020169', 'Pcs', 'single', NULL, '1740393674831913495.jpeg', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '<p>Topicure Natural Spray is an Ayurvedic proprietary veterinary medicine formulated to promote quick wound healing in livestock. Its natural ingredients help reduce infection risk, soothe irritation, and support skin regeneration. Safe for regular use on cattle, buffaloes, and other farm animals, Topicure comes in a convenient 75 ml spray bottle, making it easy to apply and maintain hygiene on the farm.<br /><br /></p>\r\n<table class=\"table table-bordered \" style=\"border-collapse: collapse; display: none; width: 100%;\">\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td style=\"width: 50%;\">Title 1</td>\r\n<td style=\"width: 50%;\">&nbsp;</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td style=\"width: 50%;\">Title 2</td>\r\n<td style=\"width: 50%;\">&nbsp;</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td style=\"width: 50%;\">Title 3</td>\r\n<td style=\"width: 50%;\">&nbsp;</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>', '<p>Topicure Natural Spray offers a holistic approach to livestock wound care, harnessing the power of Ayurvedic ingredients to speed up healing and maintain healthy skin. Designed for cattle, buffaloes, goats, and other farm animals, this proprietary veterinary medicine helps protect against infection while reducing pain and irritation. <br /><br />Each 75 ml spray bottle delivers a targeted, fine mist that covers wounds evenly, minimizing the risk of contamination. The natural herbs in Topicure support tissue regeneration, promote faster scab formation, and help prevent flies from settling on open lesions. Regular application can help keep wounds clean, reduce foul odor, and maintain overall animal well-being. <br /><br />User-friendly and safe, Topicure is ideal for both small-scale farms and larger commercial operations. Simply clean the affected area, shake the can, and spray a light layer over the wound. Reapply as directed or as needed based on veterinary advice. By choosing Topicure Natural Spray, you invest in a proven, Ayurveda-inspired solution for comprehensive topical cure&mdash;ensuring a healthier, happier life for your livestock.</p>', NULL, 1, NULL, 'Topicure Natural Spray | Ayurvedic Topical Cure for Livestock (75 ml)', '<p>Heal and protect your livestock with Topicure Natural Spray. This 75 ml Ayurvedic topical solution helps speed wound healing, reduce infection risk, and support overall skin health.</p>', 'Topicure, Natural Spray, Ayurvedic Veterinary Medicine, Livestock Wound Care, Topical Cure, Animal Wound Spray, 75 ml', NULL, '2025-02-24 10:41:14', '2025-03-23 13:00:53'),
(126, 'PetMe Nursing Bottle for Pets  Complete Feeding Kit', NULL, 0, 0, NULL, NULL, 'no', NULL, 0, 0, 0, 0, '0', 'IT020599', 'Pcs', 'single', NULL, '1740397555327398185.jpeg', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '<p>Make feeding time simpler with the PetMe Nursing Bottle for Pets. This convenient kit includes a high-quality bottle, extra nipples, and a handy cleaning brush&mdash;perfect for puppies, kittens, and other small animals. Designed for comfortable grip and easy flow control, the PetMe Nursing Bottle ensures a safe, hygienic way to nurture your furry friends during their crucial early stages.<br /><br /></p>\r\n<table class=\"table table-bordered \" style=\"border-collapse: collapse; display: none; width: 100%;\">\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td style=\"width: 50%;\">Title 1</td>\r\n<td style=\"width: 50%;\">&nbsp;</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td style=\"width: 50%;\">Title 2</td>\r\n<td style=\"width: 50%;\">&nbsp;</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td style=\"width: 50%;\">Title 3</td>\r\n<td style=\"width: 50%;\">&nbsp;</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>', '<p>The PetMe Nursing Bottle for Pets is an essential tool for pet owners and breeders looking to provide the best care for newborn or young animals. Made from durable, BPA-free materials, this nursing bottle is designed to mimic a natural feeding experience, helping puppies, kittens, and other small pets transition smoothly. The included extra nipples allow you to adjust flow rate or replace worn-out parts over time, ensuring continued hygiene and comfort for your growing pets.<br /><br />For added convenience, the set comes with a specialized cleaning brush that fits perfectly inside the bottle and nipples. This makes regular maintenance quick and hassle-free, preventing bacterial buildup and keeping your feeding kit sanitary. The ergonomic shape of the bottle offers a comfortable grip, making it easier to feed squirmy, energetic babies. <br /><br />Whether you&rsquo;re a pet owner, rescue worker, or professional breeder, the PetMe Nursing Bottle helps ensure proper nutrition and healthy development for your furry friends. With this complete kit, you can rest assured that feeding time is both efficient and enjoyable&mdash;for you and your pets alike.<br /><br /></p>', NULL, 1, NULL, 'PetMe Nursing Bottle | Ideal for Puppies, Kittens & Small Animals', '<p>Ensure safe and easy feeding for newborn pets with the PetMe Nursing Bottle. Perfect for puppies, kittens, and other small animals, it comes with extra nipples and a cleaning brush.</p>', 'PetMe Nursing Bottle, Pet Feeding Bottle, Puppies, Kittens, Newborn Pets, Small Animal Nursing, Complete Feeding Kit', NULL, '2025-02-24 11:45:55', '2025-03-16 07:46:23');
